replies.bodyText:
Actually, it will not out of order because it is in a lock. But you remind me that we should not print logs in the lock here.
Should be modified to:
{
    lock_gurad ();
    xxx.notify ()
}
LOG (...);

As for the order problem, we can print one log at the beginning of the function, which can help us to check the order when tracing problems.
In addition, we can print the total number of current queued tasks here too.

